Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:12.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, attention please?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:15.13,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Some of you may have already noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:18.32,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,but there's this little dot here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.32,0:00:20.83,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of like a secondary \Nsex characteristic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:24.55,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not pronounced \NGintama Dash or Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:26.66,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Due to grown-up circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:28.34,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:30.03,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Because grown-ups grow hair down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:32.48,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still pronounced Gintama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:35.45,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Grown-ups keep their mouths shut
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:37.08,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,when someone's unshaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.52,0:00:41.66,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So with that lesson learned, \Nlet's try this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:16.40,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Snack Otose
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:16.39,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she's got herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:20.20,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,...a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:24.45,Main02,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed that Catherine was behaving
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.99,Main02,,0000,0000,0000,,rather oddly lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:27.41,Main02,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,That explains why.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:30.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So, did someone lose a bet or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:32.36,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,He's a regular here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:34.92,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,They've been on friendly \Nterms for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:37.35,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No, seriously. This guy must have lost
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:38.43,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This defies logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:40.59,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No man would ever be interested \Nin that nasty woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:44.84,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Clearly, she was the result \Nof a bad joke by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.27,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If he threw together some \Nleftover cat and housewife parts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.31,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,to make a present for his grandchild,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.62,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,which was then relegated
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:54.92,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,to chew toy duty, that would be her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:57.33,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you think that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:02:59.27,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine-san looks prettier these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:00.29,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:02.43,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You mean how the cat and \Nhousewife parts fit together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:04.18,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's because God files \Nthe edges and gives the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.28,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,putty plenty of time to dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:07.11,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,According to my data,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:08.13,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,women become more beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:09.66,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,when they fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:10.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.83,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's just lip service.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:14.53,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they tend to place their
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.61,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,hand on their cheek and sigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:18.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Just stop already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:22.23,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Women, old and robot, \Nalways love this topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:25.13,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,My folder of love stories \Nis ten yottabytes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculously huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.04,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:29.96,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You can putty up a Zaku \Nas much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:31.82,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's never going to become a Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:33.16,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Fix your data.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:34.19,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:37.86,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Master Gintoki can never \Nbe like Hiro Mizushima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.44,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Gajiro Sato is the best he can manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:42.20,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the cruel gap \Nin wavy hair characters?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:44.20,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.48,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the Zaku's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:48.72,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Tune her up, mechanic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:51.06,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:52.45,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,There was an elderly person
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:54.53,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,who needed help carrying something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:57.75,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Please deduct it from my wages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:03.45,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Z-ZZZ Gundam has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:04.88,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I explain this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:07.02,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Explain what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:09.69,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Her physique is completely different!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:12.97,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You can't pin this on an \Nidiosyncratic animator!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:13.81,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Gintoki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.10,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:16.88,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:19.07,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Even her personality has been Newtype'd!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:21.81,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she so polite now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:24.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Love can't change a girl this much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.15,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, love...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:28.37,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,You all know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:30.45,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.44,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:33.09,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I planned to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:35.34,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,once everything was settled...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.41,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was settled?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.38,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:42.63,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Otose-san, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:48.89,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Snack Otose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:45.68,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,...in a relationship with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.74,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,someone who wants to marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:54.85,On Screen,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,It's Too Confusing When Talking About the Poster Girl for a Poster Store, So Call Her a Sandwich Board
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:58.07,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Suejiro Suemoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:00.08,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,A regular at Otose-san's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:02.43,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's how he got to know Catherine-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.66,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,He's an up-and-coming entrepreneur
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:06.91,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,with considerable influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:08.48,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:11.05,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,There are some real weirdos out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:17.42,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar Content
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.36,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,People have always sucked up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.47,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,to him because of his money,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:17.42,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,so Catherine-san was like \Na breath of fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:23.67,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:26.68,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.80,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.93,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,You should wipe off your sweat first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:34.18,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:37.94,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:44.44,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,(My, Suejiro-san is so bold.)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.45,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Flower House
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.45,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear. My head is spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:51.45,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,This is so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.08,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:54.70,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:56.83,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:57.96,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Suejiro-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:01.71,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.71,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the right show?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:08.72,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Who wants to see them \Nfawn over each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.77,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san, we should be happy for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:12.89,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That would be the grown-up response.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:13.43,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.29,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Grown-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:14.88,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:15.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:19.51,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, business is \Nbooming at Snack Otose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:22.46,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It must be the charm of \Na new wife or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:24.73,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,since Catherine-san has \Ndoubled her clientele.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.18,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And Suejiro-san seems \Nlike a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:29.24,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,He was a regular customer,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:32.13,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,so he isn't going to tell \Nher to stop working.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:33.24,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:35.02,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't fall
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.40,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,for a woman like her, Sadaharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:38.49,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You never know when she's gonna
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:40.00,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,turn back into a chew toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:33.39,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar Content
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:32.87,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,He lost all of his assets
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:35.01,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,when Lehman Brothers went bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:37.06,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,So he was saying that he can
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.64,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,no longer make Catherine-san happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:40.68,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,So he wants to call it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:42.97,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Just goes to show that he's a man with
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:44.06,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,no money and no balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.65,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But Catherine-san refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:49.82,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,She said that she would support him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:50.57,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:54.47,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Suejiro-san has a piece \Nof property left that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.60,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't in the Kabuki district.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.31,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to open a new business there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:07:59.66,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,With Catherine-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:01.39,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:02.79,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,That thief who showed up in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.22,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,episode 12 of this anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:07.64,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,is finally leaving in episode 206?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:09.42,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's like she's graduating,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.46,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,becoming independent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:15.26,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Otose-san will be a little lonely,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.03,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure that she'll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:18.50,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,one to congratulate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:21.50,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Master Gintoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:23.60,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,There is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:26.19,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Could you come see Ms. \NOtose immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:31.72,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I have a little \Nemergency of my own here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:33.57,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Could you leave immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.09,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I will take over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:36.20,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Take over what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:52.21,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the bathroom clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:39.21,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Go see Ms. Otose now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:41.08,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,After walking through the cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:44.13,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at terminal velocity, \Nor diarrhea city.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:45.39,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I have retrieved the appropriate data.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:48.61,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I simply need to continue \Nmaking ice cream, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:50.02,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:52.21,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And make sure it doesn't \Nfall off the cone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:54.01,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.97,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.71,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,She probably wants to talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:59.47,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine-san and Suejiro-san's future?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:03.31,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,-Gin-chan!\N-Gin-San!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.14,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.27,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.86,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:09.74,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,Otose-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:13.15,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to leave, scram.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:16.66,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I won't object or try to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.60,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't stand
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:22.57,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,to watch people like you who dream
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:26.33,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,and can't keep their feet on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:29.11,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.79,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,But are you really saying that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.36,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine's hopes are \Njust a pipe dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.61,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Otose-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:34.42,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:38.37,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I've been saving up money
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:42.43,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,so I might open my own bar one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:44.93,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Snack Otose
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.10,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to create a place
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:48.40,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,like this one, where \Neveryone was all smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:55.44,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to become a \Nselfless person like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.40,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I see how it is, Suejiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:02.44,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering how you could
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:03.72,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,afford to open a new business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:05.37,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,That explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.03,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:11.30,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to work together \Nfor our future...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:14.54,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and get married, \Nbe independent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.61,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need permission from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:21.43,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,We're total strangers, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.52,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Or is there more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:28.36,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,You came here because you wanted to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:31.98,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,weasel money out of me and Catherine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.23,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Otose-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.34,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's crossing the line...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:35.99,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Always...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:40.41,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought of you as my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:44.76,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, you old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:46.78,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:50.29,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm never coming back to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:52.80,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Roll over and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:54.09,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:55.74,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a lot better knowing that I won't
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:57.01,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,have to see your face again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:58.59,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:10:59.47,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not finished with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:02.38,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you that instead of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:04.01,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,You can display it in your bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.73,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be the perfect place to display
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:06.82,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,a cheap bottle of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:07.75,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,You old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:09.09,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you eat your words!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:10.98,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start up a bar that beats
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.88,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the crap out of this run-down place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:16.45,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become bigger than you ever will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.20,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:18.20,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:18.89,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:19.94,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:21.67,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:23.69,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:40.51,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Kabuki District Station
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:40.51,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Write us a letter once \Nyou're settled down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:44.35,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And invite us over \Nonce your bar is open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.01,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all come to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:49.24,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know if anything comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:51.11,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I will be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:52.52,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:55.30,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry that this isn't \Nmuch of a send-off...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:11:57.81,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Gin-san run off to this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.28,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kagura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:02.07,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You should say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:04.28,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.78,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kagura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:08.29,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,But if it's too much to take...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:12.30,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't put up with the in-laws,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.30,0:12:15.04,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,you can come back after \Nraking him for alimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:17.17,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be more than welcome then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:26.30,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Really, thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:29.86,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:32.53,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine-san, uh...\NAbout Otose-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:35.19,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,The train on Platform 2\Nwill be departing momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:37.21,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:40.28,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Suejiro-san is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:42.81,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Catherine-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:45.82,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:48.39,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,...Otose-san for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:53.83,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}Snack Otose
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.97,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you read the sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:12:59.57,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,We're closed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:00.60,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:02.18,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you don't have a choice
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:03.80,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,without your poster girl around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:06.19,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:08.16,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not here for a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:09.35,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to do the pouring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:22.56,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:26.26,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:28.37,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,she was just a dirty thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:31.29,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I felt so bad for her
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:33.97,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,that I let her stay at my bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:37.96,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,But she kept wandering off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:40.07,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't really blame her
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:42.38,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,since she was a stray at heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:46.48,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,but lately, she's settled down
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:49.35,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and been working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:53.66,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew she actually \Nhad a plan for her future...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:56.40,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't like the guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.91,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I should be grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.91,0:14:00.48,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,that anyone was willing to take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:04.45,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that she \Ncan't exactly be choosy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:06.99,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Still, as a parent...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:10.70,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Your daughter can bring \Nhome the perfect man
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.99,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,and you'll still be able \Nto find something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:15.67,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just smile and send her off,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:18.66,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,when I know she's going to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:23.50,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,That was the best I could manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:25.95,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:28.75,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,So this is how it ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:35.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel bad, don't \Ntalk like it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:40.08,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Once she's opened a bar \Nthat's as good as this one,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,you should go have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:52.26,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine, find your happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:00.92,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,The last train is departing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:07.88,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Today's service has concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:14.39,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Please exit the station \Nin a swift manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:35.56,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Suemoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:37.13,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, never heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:39.96,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there's anybody \Nby that name in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:41.46,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,A bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.01,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:46.47,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to open a drugstore here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:50.42,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Greater Edo Bank
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:52.18,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.43,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Your balance is 0 yen.\NWould you like a receipt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.54,Main01,Machine,0000,0000,0000,,Please remove your card.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.00,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Are you new here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:26.11,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you've been through,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:28.33,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's a harsh world out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.16,0:16:32.75,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,If you need anything, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:35.38,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,They call me the lord of this park.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:38.72,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything for a little alcohol...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:41.27,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Bacchus
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.27,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:44.81,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where did you get this stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:46.06,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:48.77,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lady, that's incredible stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:51.17,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Bacchus wine from Planet Bacchus,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:54.28,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,only made once every hundred years!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:58.65,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Legendary stuff that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:00.72,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,will net hundreds from any collector!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:04.78,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,H-How did you get your hands on this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:07.91,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,You can display it in your bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:10.76,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,The perfect place to display \Na cheap bottle of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:16.26,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Otose-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:19.69,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,You were giving me a push in the back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:23.58,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Otose-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:30.26,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I have no place to display \Nthis wonderful bottle...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:31.95,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I didn't drink any!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:33.20,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even take a sip!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:34.70,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I just touched the bottle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.96,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! Really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:39.27,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:39.78,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:46.33,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,So yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:48.76,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:50.35,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,what happened when I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:52.81,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,She kept saying that she
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:55.29,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,couldn't go back because she promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:58.09,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she got sick \Nof me asking questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:17:59.99,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,since she just ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:03.60,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything, Gin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.34,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hasegawa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:10.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Were your parents happy \Nwhen you got married?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:12.92,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:15.48,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,I married into money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:18.17,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,So my whole family was thrilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:19.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:23.37,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's what matters in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:28.22,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's starting, Gin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:29.46,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:30.73,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:32.44,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that's nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:34.02,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:35.30,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.38,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:39.01,Main01,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:42.89,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Easy Financing\NEvil Loans
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.89,Main01,Loan,0000,0000,0000,,You actually got the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:45.40,Main01,Loan,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.17,Main01,Loan,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to trick a few women
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.85,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and you can pay back \Nyour loan in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:19:03.12,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Evil 4 Lyfe
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:51.46,Main01,Loan,0000,0000,0000,,What was your opinion of this target,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:53.01,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,as a former gigolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:54.69,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,Quite frankly, she was so easy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:56.45,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,that I was bored to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:59.90,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,I just used her dream of opening a bar,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:01.44,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,and she completely fell for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:03.12,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:06.18,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I waste my \Ntime on that old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:09.12,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,I could barely stand \Nwalking next to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:11.85,Main01,Loan,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how you \Ncame up with the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:14.02,Main01,Loan,0000,0000,0000,,of pretending to go broke \Nafter you were a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:17.19,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,Most women will do anything for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:18.88,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,But there are a few exceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:22.52,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,who have a weakness for the penniless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:25.89,Main01,Loan,0000,0000,0000,,You're starting to look \Npretty evil yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:27.81,Main01,Loan,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you'll pay \Noff the rest in no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:30.39,Main01,Loan,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:34.89,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.89,0:19:36.05,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,We're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:37.07,Main01,Loan,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:37.90,Main01,Loan,0000,0000,0000,,Which gang is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:39.46,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:40.40,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:47.41,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Evil 4 Lyfe
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:47.41,Main01,Suejiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're the man who was at Otose's bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:49.38,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:52.42,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You guys aren't evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:55.42,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You just stole money from a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:57.57,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,who was saving up for her dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.55,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You fooled her into thinking you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:03.04,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,wanted to marry her so you \Ncould take her money...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:07.47,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make you evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:12.51,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you what true evil looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:27.14,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.68,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like having a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.19,0:20:32.92,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Are you open?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:35.42,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.58,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:40.42,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,would be open with the snow and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:43.93,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Just give me one shot \Nof your cheapest booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:59.90,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,This is a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:01.65,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,You can watch the moon, watch the snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.72,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:09.47,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,But I have one complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:14.08,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody cries while pouring a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:20.47,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,You have to have a smile \Non your face at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:24.97,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the customer is crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:31.13,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,You still have much to learn, Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.39,0:21:41.48,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.81,0:21:42.71,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:44.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I brought a little present...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:46.03,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The drinks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.01,0:21:48.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,...are on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:52.95,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine\NGreater Edo Bank
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:29.34,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.56,0:23:26.27,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.27,0:23:27.89,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pretend like these \Nglasses are Gin-san
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:29.34,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and never let them go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:30.18,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:34.97,On Screen,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Glasses Are Part of the Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:32.28,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses are part of the soul!
